{"tid":587671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果新西人有得投最後都會含柒投泛民","createTime":"2018-03-10T14:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T15:13:10.000Z","uid":175623,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d16e07711ba60222ce5112e7819aa076c8c01dee","tid":587671,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:51:54.000Z","msg":"雖然今次新西人唔洗含柒算係不幸中嘅大幸，但如果要新西人係建制泛民入面2簡1, 我最後都會含柒投泛民。<br />\n<br />\n原因：<br />\n1. 唔想比建制進1步坐大<br />\n2. 比泛民入左去點都會益到少少非建制，例如：區諾軒選到，會比政助位比黃之峰等流。<br />\n3. 長遠尼講，保住議席對下屆選舉非建制有利。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以撚你點都要含嫁啦，現實政治係咁。任何射落海，唔投票，投建制保皇都係非現實政治。"},{"pid":"1f314893519ea61377d385ca5f043e5f3d0be087","tid":587671,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:03:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"613ddf321ce97a2dc5eb67bc9962d1e808d9c95e","tid":587671,"uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:03:30.000Z","msg":"同班鍵盤狗講道理<br />\n佢地唔會明"},{"pid":"9249b25143170c27e5a61ae7905423c0ba0ccd98","tid":587671,"uid":51129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:05:29.000Z","msg":"你識咩丫<br />\n連登仔有得扮清高先係最緊要"},{"pid":"c226eb24494e4a8bdac8d054b5ea5b722e83b443","tid":587671,"uid":87573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:13:10.000Z","msg":"依家含係為左下一個男朋友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}